Contributors to the Retro OS project are encouraged to conform to the established contribution guidelines and coding standards. This promotes uniformity, code quality, and overall enhancement of Retro OS. Collaboration is crucial to maintain and augment the OS's capabilities.

7. Community Collaboration

Retro OS thrives on community collaboration. Users are encouraged to actively engage in discussions, provide constructive feedback, and contribute to the continual development and enhancement of the OS. Together, we can shape the future of Retro OS.

